uote><br />\n好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b990c3ddc6e59a228eef9fe91b134b95e9a9c5","tid":322420,"uid":122859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"你好，我地經過一番研究都係搵唔到問題既出處。<br />\n<br />\n請問你地有冇話一睇咩post先出事？例如好似睇緊留名既post？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會裝咗一啲軟件會清除瀏覧器嘅 Local Storage 資料例如 CCleaner 等等<br />\n<br />\n可以依照以下方法試下清一次 localStorage 睇下情況有冇改變。<br />\n<br />\n係網址列輸入「javascript:」再貼上 <strong>eval(atob('bG9jYWxTdG9yYWdlLmNsZWFyKCk='))</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/162313_c01d1acb21e66328e5ff1f5d90fd0382.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F162313_c01d1acb21e66328e5ff1f5d90fd0382.png&h=741da054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"defabf4fb4f39dbdf509988dc7c45406517d5523","tid":322420,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"無事WOR"},{"pid":"a817bd3b361b3e0b3642d011f66e8e980b7569df","tid":322420,"uid":4316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好，我地經過一番研究都係搵唔到問題既出處。<br />\n<br />\n請問你地有冇話一睇咩post先出事？例如好似睇緊留名既post？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會裝咗一啲軟件會清除瀏覧器嘅 Local Storage 資料例如 CCleaner 等等<br />\n<br />\n可以依照以下方法試下清一次 localStorage 睇下情況有冇改變。<br />\n<br />\n係網址列輸入「javascript:」再貼上 <strong>eval(atob('bG9jYWxTdG9yYWdlLmNsZWFyKCk='))</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/162313_c01d1acb21e66328e5ff1f5d90fd0382.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F162313_c01d1acb21e66328e5ff1f5d90fd0382.png&h=741da054&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n一陣試下先<br />\n<br />\n我用chrome 上<br />\n但每晚好準時00:00 就有error <br />\n要log out 再log in <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p